-- Merged LCD ops of Sony, rivals: eye listing by March 2016
-- 
-- Wed Aug 31, 2011 5:11am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/31/us-japan-lcd-idUSTRE77U18K20110831

 

 TOKYO  (Reuters) - A company to be created through the merger of the liquid-crystal display operations owned by Sony Corp, Toshiba Corp and Hitachi Ltd will aim to list its shares by March 2016, the firms and a government-sponsored fund said on Wednesday. 

 (Reporting by  Taiga Uranaka ; Editing by  Chris Gallagher )